      • addNewPartner

        @POST
 @Produces(value="application/json")
 @Consumes(value="application/json")
public javax.ws.rs.core.Response addNewPartner(RegistryPartner partner)
        Adds a remote instance as a registry partner. There are two entry points for this call within ICE. One is from the web of registries task. This does not contain any authentication information and therefore requires verification of the token.

        The second is from the admin ui where a partner is manually added to this ice instance.

        Parameters:
        partner - details about the partner to add

        @GET
 @Produces(value="application/json")
 @Path(value="/{id}/entries")
public javax.ws.rs.core.Response getWebEntries(@PathParam(value="id")
                                                                                                                       long partnerId,
                                                                                                                       @DefaultValue(value="0") @QueryParam(value="offset")
